Class Contact

java.lang.Object
Contact
All Implemented Interfaces:
contactsInterface, Comparable<Contact>, textColors
public class Contact extends Object implements contactsInterface, Comparable<Contact>, textColors
 Class to hold information about a contact.
 Information stored:
 * First and last name
 * Address
 * Phone number
 * Birthday
 * Any notes about the contact
